Premium "header color band" layout â€” solid or gradient colored header strip at the top with title/description, white form card BELOW that visually OVERLAPS the band edge with a negative-margin lift. Compact, corporate, professional. Best for customer surveys, support intake, B2B forms.

Canonical schema:
```json
{
  "version":"1.0",
  "title":"Customer Support Request",
  "description":"Tell us about your issue â€” we typically respond within 4 business hours.",
  "fields":[
    { "key":"row_name", "type":"Row", "columns":[
      { "span":6, "fields":[{ "key":"first_name", "type":"Text", "label":"First name", "required":true }] },
      { "span":6, "fields":[{ "key":"last_name",  "type":"Text", "label":"Last name",  "required":true }] }
    ]},
    { "key":"email", "type":"Email", "label":"Email", "required":true },
    { "key":"category", "type":"Select", "label":"Category", "required":true, "options":[
      {"value":"billing","label":"Billing"},{"value":"technical","label":"Technical"},{"value":"general","label":"General"}
    ]},
    { "key":"priority", "type":"Radio", "label":"Priority", "options":[
      {"value":"low","label":"Low"},{"value":"medium","label":"Medium"},{"value":"high","label":"High"}
    ], "properties":{"optionColumns":3} },
    { "key":"description", "type":"Textarea", "label":"Describe the issue", "required":true }
  ],
  "settings":{
    "theme":"custom",
    "submitButtonText":"Submit request",
    "customHtml":"<div class=\"mfp mfp-header-band\"><div class=\"mfp-band\"><h1 class=\"mfp-band-title\">{{form:title}}</h1><p class=\"mfp-band-sub\">{{form:description}}</p></div><div class=\"mfp-body\"><div class=\"mfp-body-inner\">{{field:row_name}}{{field:email}}{{field:category}}{{field:priority}}{{field:description}}<div class=\"mfp-submit-wrap\">{{form:submit}}</div></div></div></div>",
    "customCss":".mfp.mfp-header-band{max-width:760px;margin:32px auto 60px;font-family:'Inter',sans-serif}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mfp-band{background:linear-gradient(135deg,#1e3a8a,#3b82f6);color:#fff;padding:36px 36px 56px;border-radius:14px 14px 0 0;text-align:left}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mfp-band-title{font-size:26px;font-weight:800;margin:0 0 8px;line-height:1.2;letter-spacing:-0.01em}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mfp-band-sub{font-size:14px;opacity:0.9;margin:0;line-height:1.5}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mfp-body{background:#fff;border-radius:14px;box-shadow:0 24px 60px -20px rgba(15,23,42,0.25);margin-top:-32px;position:relative;padding:32px 36px 40px}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mfp-body-inner{display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:18px}.mfp.mfp-header-band input,.mfp.mfp-header-band textarea,.mfp.mfp-header-band select{width:100%;border:1px solid #e2e8f0;border-radius:8px;padding:11px 14px;font-size:14px;background:#fff;box-sizing:border-box}.mfp.mfp-header-band input:focus,.mfp.mfp-header-band textarea:focus{border-color:#3b82f6;box-shadow:0 0 0 3px rgba(59,130,246,0.15);outline:none}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mf-field-label{font-size:13px;font-weight:600;color:#334155;margin-bottom:6px;display:block}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mf-required{color:#ef4444}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mf-btn-submit,.mfp.mfp-header-band button[type=submit]{width:auto;background:#1e3a8a;color:#fff;border:0;padding:11px 28px;border-radius:8px;font-weight:600;font-size:14px;cursor:pointer;margin-top:8px}.mfp.mfp-header-band .mf-btn-submit:hover{background:#1e40af}@media (max-width:640px){.mfp.mfp-header-band .mfp-band,.mfp.mfp-header-band .mfp-body{padding-left:20px;padding-right:20px}}"
  }
}
```

ANATOMY:
- `.mfp-band` colored header â€” swap the gradient for any brand color. `padding-bottom:56px` is deliberately deep so the white form card overlaps it.
- `.mfp-body` white card with `margin-top:-32px` to lift up INTO the band â€” creates the signature "card sitting on the color stripe" look.
- `border-radius` arrangement: band has `14px 14px 0 0` (top corners only), body has full `14px` so they visually merge but the body stands out.
- Submit button is solid `#1e3a8a` (matching the band) instead of gradient â€” more corporate.

COLOR VARIANTS (swap the band gradient):
- Healthcare: `linear-gradient(135deg,#0f766e,#14b8a6)` (teal)
- Marketing: `linear-gradient(135deg,#ec4899,#f97316)` (pink â†’ orange)
- Finance: `linear-gradient(135deg,#1e293b,#475569)` (slate steel)
- Education: `linear-gradient(135deg,#7c3aed,#a855f7)` (deep purple)

